{"word":"βύω","slug":"βύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βύω</b></el> <p/><i>to stuff</i>,<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> rei, <i>to stuff full of</i>, only in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>νήματος βεβυσμένος</el> <i>stuffed full of</i> spun-work or yarn, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>τὸ στόμα ἐβέβυστο [</el><a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>χρυσοῦ]</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <i>to stop</i> or <i>bung up with, plug</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>σπογγίωι βεβυσμένος</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>βεβ. τὰ ὦτα</el> <i>deaf</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}